{"tid":1078862,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[WhatsApp]痴hike線2.0行山群組","createTime":"2019-03-26T14:02:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T04:28:41.000Z","uid":40883,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"f24645c82caca25b9c7214b8c92deb936aa84200","tid":1078862,"uid":40883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T14:02:04.000Z","msg":"痴hike線已成立兩年有多，多謝大家一直既支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地好耐冇加過新血，所以係到誠意邀請熱愛行山嘅巴絲打加入我地，即使你係未行過山既新手，又或者鍾意考牌、綑邊、溯澗、攀爬既高手都無任歡迎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解叫痴hike線2.0？因為我地發現每次加新會員入去時，未必個個都能夠投入舊會員的閒聊對話之中，令有心行山既會員係未出席活動前已經被閒聊信息轟炸，嚇到<br />\n退群<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以今次招人會重新開一個新既群組，歡迎想行又怕融入唔到舊群舊圈子既人加入，儲夠30人就開群<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>群組規則 </ins><br />\n<br />\n1. 需要定期出席行山活動，會定期踢走長期潛水人士<br />\n<br />\n2. 愛護郊野，不破壞生態，做個有公德既行山客<br />\n<br />\n3. 大家和睦相處，互相尊重<br />\n<br />\n4. 本群只接受行山或其他體育活動，希望吃飲玩樂既請到其他群組<br />\n<br />\n有興趣係以下網址報名！謝謝！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27bf4ba7d2a484702d09d92071c4e1fd06cd76e5","tid":1078862,"uid":76105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T14:04:15.000Z","msg":"有無打野戰活動"},{"pid":"b65d2fa78a5bc83d6e241c361b12e2f22a2f02ab","tid":1078862,"uid":40883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27bf4ba7d2a484702d09d92071c4e1fd06cd76e5","tid":1078862,"uid":76105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T14:04:15.000Z","msg":"有無打野戰活動"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T14:06:56.000Z","msg":"暫時未有<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出澗出海打水戰就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84595e6b94ae7510b8f92a141d7a02fe4ae8c58a","tid":1078862,"uid":64558,"lik